+++ About +++
A comprehensive, secure and flexible user authentication/management system for PHP 5+ using MySQLi

+++ Requirements +++
PHP 5+ as the core classes are OO
MySQLi support
MySQL 5+ database server

+++ Installation +++
1. Download
2. Unzip
3. Go to: /lib/config.php and enter the required information
4. Upload
5. Be happy

